sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant Runtime as EvSimRuntime
    participant Ramp as RampInterpolator
    participant Soc as SocIntegrator
    participant Ctx as FsmContext
    participant Iso as ISO15118_ev
    participant E2M as e2m/ev_info

    Note over Runtime,E2M: tick_fd fires every tick_interval_ms while Charging

    Runtime->>Ramp: step(ctx, now)
    Ramp->>Ctx: update charging_current_a
    Ramp->>Ctx: set_desired_ac_params

    Runtime->>Soc: step(ctx)
    Soc->>Ctx: integrate power -> battery_charge_wh
    Soc->>Iso: iso_update_soc(pct)
    Soc->>E2M: publish ev_info
